   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>The 24th year of Marcus Aurelius Severus Antoninus Parthicus Maximus Britannicus Maximus Germanicus Maximus Pius Augustus, Hathyr. Horion, son of Simourk, has paid to Ptollarion and his associates, the collectors of the annona of cheap wine of Karanis, eight drachmai, equals 8 drachmai.</ab>
